    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Records of the expenditures and activities of the churchwarden, a lay honorary officer of a parish church who manages secular affairs, particularly those relating to the church building and other property.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
